---
title: Ireland’s Truffled Pub Burgers Top recipes from HelloFresh markets around the world
description: In honor of this year’s summer games, we bring you a gold medal winner of our own! From HF Ireland, this hearty burger is infused with smoky paprika, smothered in a creamy truffled shallot gravy, and tucked into a buttery brioche bun with juicy tomato slices. Serve with golden brown potato wedges and gravy on the side for champion-level dipping!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/667ac76ee4ccb870eb4daeeb-3c36da0c.png
